id: network-bind-policy
severity: critical
description: "No agent may create services on 0.0.0.0. Internal IP or localhost only."
guard: "NO AGENT MAY BIND SERVICES TO 0.0.0.0. All service bind addresses must be 127.0.0.1 or a specific internal IP address."
rules:
  - All service bind addresses must be 127.0.0.1 or specific internal IP
  - 0.0.0.0 is FORBIDDEN for all service bindings
  - auto-remediate: replace 0.0.0.0 with internal IP in service configuration
  - scan targets: systemd service files, docker compose, server configs
